Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.58,0:01:24.28,EN - Aqours,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be11}Will you wait for me? I want to become an even better person
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.28,0:01:33.02,EN - Aqours,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be11}Love is still a far-off passion full of mystery
