Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.75,0:01:50.57,EN - Aqours,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be11}(There's so many things I'd like to learn)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.68,0:01:52.96,EN - Aqours,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be11}I'll chase after
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.69,0:01:54.68,EN - Aqours,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be11}(And look for)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.94,0:02:00.60,EN - Aqours,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be11}The one I look up to
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.08,0:02:13.64,EN - Aqours,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be11}I wonder if I could make an hourglass? My thoughts always ramble on
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.64,0:02:21.14,EN - Aqours,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be11}Whenever I'm by the sea
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.46,0:02:31.08,EN - Aqours,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be11}If I pause for a little while, alone, sadness creeps up within me
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.08,0:02:39.30,EN - Aqours,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be11}La la la... The song of love brings me to tears
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.83,0:02:44.73,EN - Aqours,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be11}Would I understand if I tried asking someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.73,0:02:48.57,EN - Aqours,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be11}It's not something you can understand by asking someone else, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.61,0:02:59.24,EN - Aqours,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be11}I want to try singing with all my might, with the power of love that scorches my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.24,0:03:02.46,EN - Aqours,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be11}(But now's not the time yet, right?)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.46,0:03:11.20,EN - Aqours,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be11}Will you believe in me? I'll definitely be able to sing it someday
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.20,0:03:19.95,EN - Aqours,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be11}The ins and outs of love, even imagining it is a mission for the future
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.95,0:03:28.63,EN - Aqours,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be11}Will you believe in me? I'll definitely be able to sing it someday
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.71,0:03:36.49,EN - Aqours,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be11}That's why, I won't overthink it
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.55,0:03:37.32,EN - Aqours,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be11}(Can I just go with the flow?)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.52,0:03:39.98,EN - Aqours,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be11}Will I...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.49,0:03:41.70,EN - Aqours,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be11}(Eventually)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.70,0:03:47.77,EN - Aqours,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be11}Encounter it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.71,0:04:10.04,EN - Aqours,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be11}The echoes of the love song
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.04,0:04:14.45,EN - Aqours,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be11}Are both kind and sad at the same time, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.45,0:04:18.82,EN - Aqours,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be11}For some reason, without me realizing it
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.82,0:04:23.18,EN - Aqours,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be11}Hey, my chest hurts
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.18,0:04:27.50,EN - Aqours,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be11}The scent of the love song
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.50,0:04:31.36,EN - Aqours,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be11}Is even bluer than the sea breeze
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.36,0:04:37.43,EN - Aqours,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be11}It's a scent I'd like to make sure of
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.43,0:04:45.05,EN - Aqours,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be11}(It's a blue and sad scent)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.05,0:04:53.74,EN - Aqours,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be11}Will you wait for me? I want to become an even better person
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.74,0:05:02.43,EN - Aqours,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be11}Love is still a far-off passion full of mystery
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.43,0:05:11.11,EN - Aqours,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be11}Will you wait for me? I want to become an even better person
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.12,0:05:18.84,EN - Aqours,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be11}That's why I want to know more
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.10,0:05:19.80,EN - Aqours,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be11}(There's so many things I'd like to learn)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.11,0:05:22.33,EN - Aqours,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be11}I'll chase after the one I look up to
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.55,0:05:23.73,EN - Aqours,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be11}(And look for)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.72,0:05:34.35,EN - Aqours,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be11}Ah, all while humming a love song...
